      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kalna ar Muheerem stiprinajſchi/ un us Laukem aiskawejanas Leetas likuschi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad avſkaitahs winſch toh- ti/ un aizſnaja wiſſis Moaba Leelus Kungus/ un wiſſus Am- mona Waldneekus/ un wiſſus Walditajus to Walstu/ kas Juha- ras puffē bija/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiſsch fazzija uſ teem: Stahſtajt man jelle juhs Kana- niteri/ kahdi tee Laudis irr/ kas us tahm Kalnu Weetahm dſih- wo? un kahdt tee Pilsfahți/eekſch ka tee dſihwo/ un zik leels winnu Karra Spehks irr? un kahda winnu Warra un winnu Spehks? Kutsch winkeem par Kehniinu jeb Leelu Kungu win- an Karra Spehka irr?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un kapehz turrahſ tee wat- rak pretti/ ka wiſſi/ kas prett Wakkara puffi dſihwo/ ka tee man pretti ne nahk?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija us to Arioks tas Waldneeks pahr wiſſeem Ammona Behrxeem: Klansi jelle/ mans Kungs to Wallodu no tawa Kalpa Muttes/ jo ce ſtahſtischu tew to Pateefibu pahr ſcheem Laudim/ kas us ſchihm Kalnu Weetahm dſihwo/ un tu- wu pee terwis miht/ un Melli ne ſees no tawa Kalpa Muttee.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Schee Laudis irr weens Dſimmuns no teem Kaldeereem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un bija pirnak par Eebu- weeſcheem eekſch Mesopotami- jas/ jo tee ne gribbeja fawu Wezz Tehwu Deetweein kla-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "fiht/ kas Kaldeeru Semme bija. Bet tee pamette fawu Wezzaku Eeraschas/ un peeluh- dſe to Deewu no Debbes/ ko tee bij atſinnuschi: Un kad tee tohs preekſch faweem Deeweem iſ- dfinne/ tad behdſe tee uhs Meso- potamiju/ un bija tur Eebuwee- ſchôs igu Laiku.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiſſau Deews paweh- leja/ ka teem bij iſeet no fawas Eebuweetibas un us to Semmi Kanaan eet/ un tur tee dſihwo- ja/ un famantoja dauds Selta un Sudraba un lohti dauds Lohpus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad nogahje tee us Egip- ti/ jo eekſch Kanāāna Seimmes bija Bads/ un mahjoja tur/ ka- mehr tee atkah atnahze; un ktua tur par leelu Pulku/ ta ka win- nu Dſimmums ne bijisskaitams.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet tas Egiptes Reh- ninsch usſtahweja prett win- keem/ ka tee tohs ar Wiltn no- mehrdetu/ un ar Gruhtumu un ar Keegekn Darbu/ un tee pa- femmaja tohs/ un darrija tohs par Kalveem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tee brehze us fatwu Deewu/ un tas fitte wiſſu E- giptes Semmi ar Mohzibahm/ pee ka Dseedinaschanas ne bija: Tad iſdfinne tee Egiptei tohs no ſerwig ahra.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Deews iſſchaweja winnu Preekſcha to farlanu Juhru.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un waddija tohs pee ta Kalna Sinajus/ un us Kades Bar-\n"
    }
  ],
